b'Sakura Nagashi': b'Singer Hikaru Utada\'s YouTube channel began streaming a music video for her song "Sakura Nagashi," the theme song for Evangelion: 3.33 You Can (Not) Redo, set to scenes from the film. The music video features cuts that were not used in the original film. The video was available for 24 hours.\n\n(Source: ANN)'
